    {
      "text": "The compound shown in the image can be used in the treatment of which of the following poisonings?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Aluminum Phosphide\nB) Mercury\nC) Phosphorus\nD) Arsenic"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Mercury"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Phosphorus"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Arsenic"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<p>Copper <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"535af9a2181692777199309af44d24\">sulfate</span> acts as an <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"04777bad221692777194ecaf496e16\">oxidizing agent</span> and converts elemental <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"bfea0730ac16927771959eb551740f\">phosphorus</span> into less toxic compounds. It is specifically used in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"bfea0730ac16927771959eb551740f\">phosphorus</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> cases.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Aluminum <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c7ee01df1b169277719539ad796de7\">Phosphide</span> (Option A):</strong> Aluminum <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c7ee01df1b169277719539ad796de7\">phosphide</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> is treated with supportive care, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4d7ed0baae169277719199f6e9ab7b\">magnesium</span> sulfate, and antioxidants.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Mercury (Option B):</strong> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b59bbde2f816927771924bb2b17b64\">Mercury</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> is treated with chelating agents such as dimercaprol, succimer, or DMSA.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Arsenic (Option D): </strong>Arsenic <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> is treated with chelators like <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"33991687cf16927771860916b1f69e\">dimercaprol</span> or succimer.</p>\n\n<p> </p>",
      "question_images": [
        "https://image.prepladder.com/content/mh2bSbhBWjyrfoAjP2Ow1741789308.png"
      ],
      "explanation_video": null,
      "explanation_images": [],
      "explanation_audio_eng": null,
      "explanation_audio_hin": null
    },
    {
      "text": "A student presents with shock, pulmonary edema, and a positive silver nitrate breath test after consuming an unknown substance. What is the antidote?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "BAL"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Pralidoxime"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "MgSO₄"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Atropine"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<ul>\n\t<li>The silver <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ad09a76257169277719349e2735418\">nitrate</span> breath test detects <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"98074ba090169277719565a262e2e0\">phosphine</span> gas, confirming aluminum <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c7ee01df1b169277719539ad796de7\">phosphide</span> poisoning.</li>\n\t<li>Aluminum <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c7ee01df1b169277719539ad796de7\">phosphide</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> releases <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"98074ba090169277719565a262e2e0\">phosphine</span> gas, which causes severe mitochondrial dysfunction, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f3739d892c1692777184b2e134615c\">circulatory</span> collapse, and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"10e2dee19e1692777196673db90c23\">pulmonary</span> edema.</li>\n\t<li>Magnesium <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"535af9a2181692777199309af44d24\">sulfate</span> stabilizes myocardial membranes and helps counteract hypomagnesemia, a common complication.</li>\n\t<li>Management includes supportive care (fluids, vasopressors, oxygen therapy), <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4d7ed0baae169277719199f6e9ab7b\">magnesium</span> sulfate, and antioxidants.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Antidotes and their mechanisms</strong></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:624px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Poisoning Type</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Antidote</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Mechanism</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Arsenic</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>BAL (Dimercaprol) <strong>(Option A ruled out)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>IM, chelates arsenic for excretion.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Succimer (DMSA)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Oral chelation.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>DMPS</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>IV, transitioned to oral chelation.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Copper</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Potassium Ferrocyanide</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Forms <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5d21b8a47c16927771906f7f0e2590\">insoluble</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> complexes, reducing absorption.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Penicillamine</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Chelates copper.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"4\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Cyanide</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Sodium Nitrite</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Forms <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4b68d201f1169277719205f9339df9\">methemoglobin</span> to bind cyanide.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Sodium Thiosulfate</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Converts <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"2cf30efe831692777185e200487656\">cyanide</span> to <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5aa5b842b01692777200b64c672a29\">thiocyanate</span> for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b9356afdba16927771979d068c6587\">renal</span> excretion.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Hydroxocobalamin</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Binds cyanide, forming cyanocobalamin.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Dicobalt Edetate, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f1f83adcbd1692777192944952fb13\">Methylene</span> Blue</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Alternative antidotes.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Ethylene Glycol</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Ethanol/Fomepizole</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Inhibits <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4c1279cdf1169277718118b18c10ab\">alcohol dehydrogenase</span> to prevent toxic metabolites.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Iron</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Desferrioxamine</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Chelates iron for excretion.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Magnesium Hydroxide/Sodium Bicarbonate</p>\n\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Note:</strong> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"eff14f005f16927771826bf88cb6c5\">BAL</span> should not be used in iron, cadmium, or <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e379f984b316927771986bb72f5402\">selenium</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> due to formation of toxic complexes.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Precipitate iron, reducing absorption.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Lead</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Sodium/Magnesium Sulfate</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Forms <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5d21b8a47c16927771906f7f0e2590\">insoluble</span> lead sulfate.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Calcium Chloride/Gluconate</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Promotes bone deposition of lead.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>CaNa2EDTA + BAL</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Chelation therapy for lead elimination.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Mercury</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Sodium <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"59e3af5975169277720384661ff5bf\">Formaldehyde</span> Sulfoxylate</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Reduces toxic <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b59bbde2f816927771924bb2b17b64\">mercury</span> ions.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>BAL (Dimercaprol)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Traditional chelator; oral agents preferred.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Methanol</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Ethanol/Fomepizole</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Compete for alcohol dehydrogenase, preventing toxic metabolites.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Opium</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Naloxone</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Blocks <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e22dbf6c52169277719441ac94a69e\">opioid</span> receptors, reversing <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e22dbf6c52169277719441ac94a69e\">opioid</span> effects.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Organophosphate</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Atropine <strong>(Option D ruled out)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Blocks <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0ad3c97c2916927771938768dcf298\">muscarinic</span> receptors to manage <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"8656dac49a16927771846b41f8cf19\">cholinergic</span> symptoms.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Pralidoxime (2-PAM) <strong>(Option B ruled out)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Reactivates acetylcholinesterase.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Phenol</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Magnesium Sulfate</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Absorbs <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0d5565e4a1169277719596227ebffd\">phenol</span> in the stomach.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Phosphorus</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Potassium Permanganate</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Oxidizes <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"bfea0730ac16927771959eb551740f\">phosphorus</span> into harmless phosphates.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Strychnine</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Barbiturates</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Depress CNS, preventing seizures.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Thallium</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Prussian Blue</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Binds <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"482583c9b71692777200e3f13d54bb\">thallium</span> in the intestine, preventing absorption.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>",
