      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 1,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct option B - <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"55164fe9f9169277718979ac034040\">Hydrocarbon</span> poisoning</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Gastric lavage, also commonly called stomach pumping or <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"12347b15191692777188bc86d226e1\">gastric</span> irrigation, is the process of cleaning out the contents of the stomach.</li>\n\t<li>It is typically used in cases of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> or drug overdose. However, there are certain conditions in which <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"12347b15191692777188bc86d226e1\">gastric</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b625b3e881169277719169ef4e1af3\">lavage</span> is contraindicated. In this case, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"12347b15191692777188bc86d226e1\">gastric</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b625b3e881169277719169ef4e1af3\">lavage</span> is contraindicated in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"55164fe9f9169277718979ac034040\">hydrocarbon</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> (Option B).</li>\n\t<li>Hydrocarbons, such as gasoline, kerosene, or petroleum-based solvents, have a low <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"2313fc54841692777202a008c72950\">viscosity</span> and can easily <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a246c8382816927771821a267ea486\">aspirate</span> into the lungs during <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"12347b15191692777188bc86d226e1\">gastric</span> lavage, leading to serious complications like <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e3510b7f981692777184c731703ebd\">chemical pneumonitis</span> or <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"831d67ad8a1692777182763ca62e4b\">aspiration</span> pneumonia.</li>\n\t<li>Therefore, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"12347b15191692777188bc86d226e1\">gastric</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b625b3e881169277719169ef4e1af3\">lavage</span> should not be performed in cases of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"55164fe9f9169277718979ac034040\">hydrocarbon</span> ingestion.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Incorrect options:</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Option A:</strong> Organo-Phosphate <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> (Option A): <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"12347b15191692777188bc86d226e1\">Gastric</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b625b3e881169277719169ef4e1af3\">lavage</span> is indicated in cases of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"505a21f8451692777194a113951c68\">organophosphate</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> to remove the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"41329dc9381692777200a9b6d57cf4\">toxin</span> from the stomach.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Option C:</strong> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f0705db1901692777187acdc0f9e24\">Ethanol</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> (Option C):  Gastric <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b625b3e881169277719169ef4e1af3\">lavage</span> is indicated in cases of Ethanol poisoning to remove the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"41329dc9381692777200a9b6d57cf4\">toxin</span> from the stomach.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Option D:</strong> PCM <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"d3323d4b271692777200122ea879e5\">toxicity</span> (Option D): PCM <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"d3323d4b271692777200122ea879e5\">toxicity</span> refers to <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"072b8af16e1692777196f21b086f92\">poisoning</span> with <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"fcdd3383341692777194cf2cd4e400\">paracetamol</span> (acetaminophen). <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"12347b15191692777188bc86d226e1\">Gastric</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b625b3e881169277719169ef4e1af3\">lavage</span> is indicated in cases of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"fcdd3383341692777194cf2cd4e400\">paracetamol</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3f4eecb1c6169277719459c801fb19\">overdose</span> within 4 hours of ingestion.</p>",
